sma lamotrigine levels should be monitored more closely whenever estrogen- and/or progestin-containing drugs are added to or withdrawn from therapy, and the lamotrigine dosage adjusted as necessary.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/18591/', '', 'Tiagabine, Ethotoin, Brivaracetam, Cannabidiol, Methsuximide, Ezogabine, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Fenfluramine, Phensuximide, Ganaxolone, More', 'Megestrol acetate, Dienogest, Bazedoxifene, Prasterone, Methyltestosterone, Megestrol acetate, Ulipristal, Dienogest, Nafarelin, Octreotide, Elagolix, More', 1767369485);
